  <div class="content"><p><img src="top-left.jpg" width="215" height="70" /><br><br>This is the site of the BuzzMonitor&trade;, an open source aggregator originally conceived and sponsored by the World Bank and co-developed by the <a href="http://www.worldbank.org" target=_blank>World Bank</a>, <a href="http://www.developmentseed.org" target=_blank>Development Seed</a> and the <a href="http://www.wri.org" target=_blank>World Resources Institute</a>. </p>

